    reversedMeaning: "Reversed, the Ace of Wands indicates creative blocks, false starts, or delays in launching a new project. The spark is there but cannot catch fire — perhaps due to fear, poor timing, or lack of focus. You may be sitting on a great idea without the motivation to execute it. Reconnect with what excites you.",
    loveMeaning: "In love, the Ace of Wands signals a passionate new attraction or a reignited spark in an existing relationship. Expect flirtation, desire, and the thrilling electricity of new romantic energy. If single, someone exciting is about to enter your orbit.",
